{"tid":622404,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺見到鬼，覺得有鬼既人，只係心中有鬼？","createTime":"2018-04-09T06:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T11:20:33.000Z","uid":123335,"like":27,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5bd083a874038ab1c511ef154c3558b565b9baac","tid":622404,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:26:49.000Z","msg":"我細過果陣都驚鬼<br />\n有時暗暗地靜靜地<br />\n就會疑神疑鬼，覺得涼涼地，好似有鬼咁<br />\n<br />\n自從我變喪左<br />\n多左做運動，做gym 練大隻，練得膽大之後<br />\n就唔再覺得有鬼<br />\n<br />\n根本鬼由心生<br />\n鬼都係弱者諗出黎既野"},{"pid":"b952a611e8a5f56257b20d53cd6174f8e337bcb2","tid":622404,"uid":70487,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:29:18.000Z","msg":"中共派落黎咁多鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2432154309156c775c423f2bfdc6cd717cb0bda","tid":622404,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:29:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"086b0621700da2022e9c232e101f8a8b480abd5b","tid":622404,"uid":123335,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f2432154309156c775c423f2bfdc6cd717cb0bda","tid":622404,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:29:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:31:55.000Z","msg":"人只要夠惡  夠大膽 夠喪<br />\n你會發覺，根本一隻鬼都冇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你只會見到一個弱肉強食既世界"},{"pid":"257f10d9285f569601d9fd83b898a32ccd28cd4a","tid":622404,"uid":178429,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:37:32.000Z","msg":"我一直唔信有鬼<br />\n認同係心中有鬼<br />\n但自己一個睇鬼片都會驚驚地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735125f1987edb720ecc705eb32eb85c9095b7b2","tid":622404,"uid":57962,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:38:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf81f7d6273c35af8879d8a7d108cc7cb4f0fb0f","tid":622404,"uid":619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:40:26.000Z","msg":"唔覺，真係見過<br />\n無想像